
LECTURE: Type Conversion and Coercion
  Type convertion : 
      To converting one type into another type of variable 
        ex : 
                   
          const getAge = prompt(Enter your age); // prompt value is always a string  , so convert into a number
          const Age = Number(getAge); // converts string   into a number
          
          const strAge = String(Age);
      
  Type coercion : 
      To detect types and do operations automatically , To understand about the coercion is must.      



        1. Predict the result of these 5 operations without executing them:
        -------------------------------------------------------------------------
        '9' - '5';
        '19' - '13' + '17';
        '19' - '13' + 17;
        '123' < 57;
        5 + 6 + '4' + 9 - 4 - 2;


        2. Execute the operations to check if you were right
        -----------------------------------------------------

        4
        617
        23
        false
        1143
